joseph decamp november 5 , 1858 - february 11 , 1923 american painter . 
bear cincinnati , ohio , study frank duveneck city . 
second half 1870s go duveneck fellow student royal academy munich , spend time florence , italy , return boston 1883 . 
become know member boston school lead edmund charles tarbell emil otto grundmann , focus figure painting , 1890s adopt style tonalism . 
founder ten american painters , group american impressionists , 1897 . 
1904 fire boston studio destroy several hundred early painting , include nearly landscape . 
die boca grande , florida . 
